## Overview
Backend-focused medical inventory management system designed to model real hospital workflows with batch-level tracking, expiry handling, and safe stock operations.

## Planned Architecture
- Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB
- Frontend: React
- Authentication: JWT

## Key Features (In Progress)
- Batch-level medicine tracking with expiry dates
- FEFO (First-Expire-First-Out) stock issuance logic
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Transaction-safe stock in/out operations
- Immutable audit logs

## Development Status
This repository is actively under development.  
Backend and frontend code will be added incrementally.
